OL,6,FMrs Rawle told a friend she was
OL,7,Fconsidering divorce and was "fed up of
OL,8,Fwaiting" just hours before allegedly
OL,9,Fstabbing him in the back, the court
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FThe defendant sent a series of text
OL,13,Fmessages to Alison Gilbert on August
OL,14,F21 2022.
OL,16,FShe told her friend she wanted to "get
OL,17,Fmy fair share" and needed to "move
OL,18,Fquickly".
