OL,3,CCouple would 'swear at each other' in
OL,4,Cfront of granddaughter, trial told
OL,6,F"I am fed up of waiting," she said in
OL,7,Fone message. "Everything is waiting,
OL,8,Fwaiting, waiting."
OL,10,FGiving evidence in court, Ms Gilbert
OL,11,Fsaid she believed her friend felt
OL,12,F"trapped" in her marriage.
OL,14,F"She just wanted out. She was trying
OL,15,Fto find a way. Her main concern was
OL,16,Falways her animals. She didn't want to
OL,17,Flose her animals."
OL,19,FMs Gilbert said she was concerned Mrs
OL,20,FRawle might try to take her own life.
