OL,6,FThe court heard Mrs Rawle, now aged
OL,7,F70, was suffering from physical health
OL,8,Fproblems and depression.
OL,10,F"She discussed getting a divorce
OL,11,Fwithout a solicitor," Ms Gilbert said.
OL,12,F"She could not afford a divorce, and
OL,13,Fhe would never agree to one anyway."
OL,15,FA few hours after those messages, Mrs
OL,16,FRawle called Ms Gilbert to tell her
OL,17,FIan Rawle was dead.
