OL,6,FDefence barrister Clare Wade KC asked
OL,7,FMrs Melville: "Did you call the police
OL,8,Fbecause you were locked out of your
OL,9,Fown property by your common law
OL,10,Fhusband?"
OL,12,FMrs Melvile confirmed this was the
OL,13,Fcase, and agreed that the police
OL,14,Fattended and confiscated his shotguns
OL,15,Fand shotgun certificates.
OL,17,FMrs Melvile said Mr Rawle never
OL,18,Fthreatened her with the weapons.
OL,20,FChristine Rawle denies murder. The
OL,21,Ftrial continues.
